## Notes

When working on this I decided to not use vite and strucure the files myself. I wanted a deeper understanding of knowing how to structure my files. Which made it harder to use picocss since I could not do simple npm install since @use "pico" would not work. Also was still having trouble grasping the difference between server.js and route.js. I did not understand how they were connected. After many hours I finally understood and have a good understanding now. Overall learned a lot. 

